posts.subject: Halo
posts.body:
So I know that they are starting to port over the old Halo games to the PC, but what are people's unadultered opinions on the Halo franchise of video games? 

Were this 8chan I'd get shitposted to oblivion for even asking that, but in an attempt to add something to the pot for discourse I'd like to have an actual conversation about the pros and cons of each game that has been released thus far.

In my particular order of enjoyment from the games I've got:
Halo 3 > Halo 2 > Halo Reach > Halo CE(PC) > Halo Wars > Halo 4 > Halo 5

Also if by some miracle one of JewJew's posse or JJ himself made it to our bunker can you please **talk to me I am lonely and I want to play Gaylo Online ;_;**

posts.subject: Garry's Mod Spying on players
posts.body:

Even if the game wasn't just and admin-abuse circle jerk of DarkRP, why all of a sudden does FacePunch want to implement this garbage? They obviously have a very SJW stance with regards to their prior big stink on their survival game Rust what with people not being able to choose their player characters and then retorting to the customers who complained with something along the lines of "Well now you know what it's like to be born in the wrong gender/race/skin" etc.
